<XMLDocContent PageName="ExodusSDK.DeviceInterface.IDeviceInfo" Title="IDeviceInfo interface" xmlns="http://www.exodusemulator.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The IDeviceInfo interface is used by the system to retrieve information on devices that are exposed by plugins. A plugin exports the
      GetDeviceEntry function, through which the system can retrieve information on the defined devices in that plugin by sending an IDeviceInfo
      object to that function to retrieve the device info.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
